278 void ArmUsInfoReal::calculate_motor_velocities()
279 {
280  // Joint mode
281  if (MoveMode == MovementMode::Joint)
282  {
283  if (JointControlled == 1)
284  {
285  MotorVelocities.m1 = JointCommand;
286  MotorVelocities.m2 = -JointCommand;
287  }
288  else if (JointControlled == 2)
289  {
290  MotorVelocities.m1 = JointCommand;
291  MotorVelocities.m2 = JointCommand;
292  }
293  else
294  {
295  MotorVelocities.set(JointCommand, JointControlled);
296  }
297 
298  // if (!MotorVelocities.checkIfNull())
299  // {
300  // ROS_INFO("Joint commands :");
301  // MotorVelocities.print();
302  // }
303  }
304 
305  // Cartesian mode
306  else if (MoveMode == MovementMode::Cartesian)
307  {
308  Vector3f velocities = { 0.f, 0.f, 0.f };
309  int singularMatrix = 0;
310 
311  // Call inverse kinematic calculation service, return velocities of first 3 motors and if matrix is singular
312  bool service_success = static_cast<bool>(mf_call_inv_kin_calc_service(velocities, singularMatrix));
313  if (service_success == false)
314  {
315  ROS_ERROR("Inverse kinematic calculation service not called");
316  }
317 
318  // ROS_INFO("--------------------------------------------------");
319  // ROS_INFO("Velocities: %f, %f, %f, %f", velocities.x, velocities.y, velocities.z, velocities.a);
320  // ROS_INFO("Singular matrix: %d", singularMatrix);
321  // ROS_INFO("--------------------------------------------------");
322 
323  MotorVelocities.m1 = (velocities.x + velocities.y) / 2;
324  MotorVelocities.m2 = (velocities.x - velocities.y) / 2;
325  MotorVelocities.m3 = velocities.z;
326  }
327 };
